{"tid":265494,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"IT 業裁員只是開始？ 傳統品牌．新興科技難幸免","createTime":"2017-05-31T16:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T16:10:38.000Z","uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdfc51b01a1f41ae49eab9b4e1237ccd6100062e","tid":265494,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"【e-zone 專訊】2017 年過了不足半個月，全球科技公司傳出裁員消息，部分更已「落實」；即使是中國經濟因素、火紅的 VR（虛擬實境）技術也難擋經濟循環的巨輪。繼中興通訊（ZTE）本周初宣布裁員約 3,000 人後，儲存方案商 Seagate Technology（希捷科技）亦宣布將關閉中國蘇州工廠，並裁員 2,000 多人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/it-%E6%A5%AD%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%8E%E6%96%B0%E8%88%88%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%9B%A3%E5%B9%B8%E5%85%8D/1222-17266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Farticle%2Fit-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25EF%25BC%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E5%2585%258D%2F1222-17266&d=sUc5KZ8H5SHklGhWMu8F%2B8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=881d9fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/it-%E6%A5%AD%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%8E%E6%96%B0%E8%88%88%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%9B%A3%E5%B9%B8%E5%85%8D/1222-17266</a>"}]}